\c 41
\s Munyengetero pakurwara
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Akakomborerwa ane hanya navarombo Jehovha achamurwira nomusi wezvakaipa.
\v 2 Jehovha achamuchengeta nokumuraramisa,	 achakomborerwa panyika; Hamungamuisi pakuda kwavavengi vake,
\v 3 Jehovha achamutsigira panhoo yourwere; Munoshandura nhoo dzake dzose pakurwa kwake.
\v 4 Ini ndakati, "Jehovha, ndinzwirei tsitsi; Poresai mweya wangu; nokuti ndakakutadzirai."
\v 5 Vavengi vangu vanotaura zvakaipa pamusoro pangu, vachiti, "Uchagofa riniko, zita rake rirove?
\v 6 Kana mumwe achiuya kuzondiona, anotaura zvisina maturo; Mwoyo wake unozviunganidzira zvakaipa; Kana obuda kumwe, anozviparidza.
\v 7 Vose, vanondivenga, vanoita zeve-zeve pamwechete pamusoro pangu; Vanoranena kunclikuvadza,
\p
\v 8 Chinhu chakaipa chakamunamatira ndizvo zvavanotaura;
\s Zvino zvaavata pasi, haachazomukizve.
\p
\v 9 Haiwa, kunyange shamwari yangu chaiyo, wandaivimba naye, aidya zvokudya zvangu,
\s Naiye andisimudzira chichitsinho chake.
\p
